                    <li>We strongly recommend completing the theory course before attending the practical week.</li>
                    <li>If you haven‚Äôt completed the theory yet, you can join our <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"  href="/courses/coastal-skipper-package">10-day Coastal Skipper Combination Course</a>:
